The new `Table`.`geometry` positions can be calculated like so:

```objc
float new_css_x   =   (self.frame.origin.x / scrollView.frame.size.width) * 100;
float new_css_y   =   (self.frame.origin.y / scrollView.frame.size.height) * 100;
```

